name: Metaverse Magazine Edition 4
description: Edition four was launched 9/14/21, featuring work from That's Nifty Podcast, Degenz, Regenz, The Purple Valley, STACY, Henrikauu, Smoochies, Ivo Lazaro, G'EVOLs, Sagaland and Parallel. Includes a custom takeover cover from Pixel Portraits and an exclusive interview with Tommy K. We also continue the TezRobots x Metaverse Magazine collab!
